meta {
  name: control the server clock for deterministic time-based testing
  type: http
  seq: 9
}

put {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/mockserver/clock
  body: json
  auth: inherit
}

headers {
  Content-Type: application/json
}

body:json {
  {
    "action": "freeze",
    "instant": "2026-01-15T10:00:00Z"
  }
}

docs {
  Freeze, advance, or reset MockServer's internal clock. The controllable clock affects response template date/time helpers (now_iso_8601, now_epoch, now_rfc_1123, dates.*) and expectation TimeToLive expiry. Event-log timestamps and JWT issuance are not affected.
  
  clock action to perform
  
  Full API reference: https://www.mock-server.com/mock_server/mockserver_clients.html
}
